{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 27,
  "title": "第二十七章（巧用）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "善行無轍迹，"
    },
    {
      "text": "善言無瑕讁，"
    },
    {
      "text": "善數不用籌策，"
    },
    {
      "text": "善閉無關楗而不可開"
    },
    {
      "text": "善結無繩約而不可解。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人常善救人，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故無棄人；"
    },
    {
      "text": "常善救物，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故無棄物。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂襲明。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故善人者，不善人之師；"
    },
    {
      "text": "不善人者，善人之資。"
    },
    {
      "text": "不貴其師，"
    },
    {
      "text": "雖智大迷，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂要妙。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善行道者求之於身，不下堂，不出門，故無轍迹。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善言謂擇言而出之，則無瑕疵讁過於天下。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善以道計事者，則守一不移，所計不多，則不用籌策而可知也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善以道閉情欲、守精神者，不如門戶有關楗可得開。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善以道結事者，乃可結其心，不如繩索可得解也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人所以常教人忠孝者，欲以救人性命。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "使貴賤各得其所也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人所以常教民順四時者，欲以救萬物之殘傷。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人不賤名而貴玉視之如一。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人善救人物，是謂襲明大道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人之行善者，聖人即以為人師。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "資，用也。人行不善者，聖人猶教導使為善，得以給用也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "獨無輔也。不愛其資 無所使也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖自以為智。言此人乃大迷惑。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能通此意，是謂知微妙要道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
